\subtree{
\title{Quality Checklist}
\p{Before concluding analysis:}

\ul{
\li{[ ] Probed all zero/empty/null edge cases}
\li{[ ] Verified defaults are secure}
\li{[ ] Checked for algorithm/mode selection footguns}
\li{[ ] Tested type confusion between security concepts}
\li{[ ] Considered all three adversary types}
\li{[ ] Verified error paths don't bypass security}
\li{[ ] Checked configuration validation}
\li{[ ] Constructor params validated (not just defaulted) - see [config-patterns.md](references/config-patterns.md#unvalidated-constructor-parameters)}
}
}
}